big areas in my view.

00:01:29.860 --> 00:01:32.130
Well, there's probably
more, but these

00:01:32.130 --> 00:01:34.690
are kind of most famous,
I would say, areas

00:01:34.690 --> 00:01:38.390
where quantitative
skills can be--

00:01:38.390 --> 00:01:39.740
are very valuable in finance.

00:01:39.740 --> 00:01:42.820
And the two areas are--
one area is statistics,

00:01:42.820 --> 00:01:45.660
predictions, which
is essentially,

00:01:45.660 --> 00:01:49.630
say given some historical
behavior in the market,

00:01:49.630 --> 00:01:53.910
how do we predict what
will happen in the future?

00:01:53.910 --> 00:01:56.620
And that's certainly
a huge industry.

00:01:56.620 --> 00:02:00.640
People have made a ton of money
